      "review_summary": "The PR adds a bounded Claude web usage fetch deadline, updates CLI timeout parsing/help and timeout exit-code mapping, allows Claude auto fallback on Linux, and adds focused timeout/fallback tests.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-reproducible: the PR merge result still calls Claude web-session availability during strategy resolution before the new deadline starts. I did not run live provider probes because AGENTS.md warns they can trigger Keychain or browser-cookie prompts.",
